## Priority Summary

| Priority | Issue | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| 🔴 Critical | No global error handler | Add Express error middleware |
| 🔴 Critical | No 404 catch-all | Add fallthrough route |
| 🔴 Critical | No security headers | Add `helmet` |
| 🟠 High | No rate limiting | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| 🟠 High | No body size limit | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| 🟠 High | Hardcoded port | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| 🟡 Medium | No auth on `/users` | Add auth middleware |
| 🟡 Medium | No request logging | Add `morgan` |
| 🟡 Medium | No CORS policy | Add explicit `cors()` config |

